Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face suddenly changed, Mr. Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm making this face because I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,another favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's not something I can talk about with a plain face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are quite alike in nature aside from a minuscule difference:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people we happened upon along the way. That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no chances. The way things work never changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like how your legwork can never defeat a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the law of nature. Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coercive power decides the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll be using this and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, with that, I will win the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You snicker contemptuously at people a lot. Do you ever look yourself in the mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grins resemble those of the skulls in the Day of the Dead festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you noticed it, little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here carrying guns all the way from the Netherworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My team, your chief, those soldiers—everyone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, little lady, offer some marigolds\Nand tequila when you visit our graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, after you meet your pathetic fate here in the outskirts of Asia,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll at least offer some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes! Take my oiler's cock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab it and get ready for the sucking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked with the Japanese man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did so with the gunslinger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of getting pushed around by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Young Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kids are fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, never mind Rock, but where's Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought she was having a chat with the small maid,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then she shut herself in a bow cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Fabiola.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you thought I went insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of everyone pushing me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola, you also met Roberta, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief was, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts me to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even if she successfully brings down the enemies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she will remember for what reason and for whom she killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.83,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, she is in a state of confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:05:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Roberta's ultimate motive is to atone for her sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief is so earnest yet uncouth, dismissing the compromised morality of murder as hypocrisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fabiola, listen carefully. This is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save her at all costs. This is my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese man might be manipulating me, but if it helps me achieve my goal, I will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to return to Venezuela before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm left alone, I will save Roberta and make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will become her cane and walk with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, I'm taking this talk beyond our master-\Nservant relationship. Listen with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief will probably stay that way. Actually,\Nit may have become a whole lot worse by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is serious! Even if we manage to\Nreturn together, the suffering will remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't stop me, Fabiola.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're really determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I thought you'd have given up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how badly Chief broke down, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be good-natured and diligent, but you're still a spoiled little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you couldn't handle this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're still going to do it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I won't let her die a dog's death in their hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it! I'm sure we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely. May the Lord bless us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the Lord bless us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Family love? She's got her head in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one was ever there to protect me when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:07:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. What the hell? Damn it. Damn it. Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you. Die. Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you. Just die. Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucker. Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky, I need alcohol so get your ass—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck this. What a terrible flashback.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We entered the Mekong Delta on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd see the blue water had changed\Nto brown if the sun were up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! This stench reminds me of my U.S. brown-water navy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'd rather pass by this place\Nin the dead of night like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The GPS and the echo sounder are\Nall we can depend on from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm looking through the latest survey data of a mining company.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also worried that we can't travel\Nas fast in this shallow water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maid is rapidly catching up to us this very second. Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ, I'm fucking anxious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese man told me you were waiting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something you gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes tell me that you won't forget what I've done, that you'll never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to shoot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that way, Major,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please listen to me for the sake\Nof the justice you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:09:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the responsibility for what happened to you, your father, and your maid falls only on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My men will engage in battle ordinarily\Nand protect themselves. Will that be fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you infuse in Young Master's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you half of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, we will reach the area of operation tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, expect the woman that came after us in Roanapur to be there. This is for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy all obstacles in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that woman related to this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I alone will bear that responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give your all for the mission and for justice. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we overcome this situation without betting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were looking ahead to all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm eliminating every factor other than luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a standard gambling tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gamble is at its finest when winning is a matter of trying one's luck at the very last moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, sirs, right in the center\Nof the border of three countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the area of a three-way standoff that no one dares break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Golden Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need. I already got paid in full for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for acting rather unfriendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good hunting! And try not to drag us into your mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Garcia leave with the Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going to hit the jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Benny, he's going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chang is going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo to Alpha. We've reached the sentry location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Situation OK. No coordinate changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alpha, roger. Standby for orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Delta. Two hundred yards to sentry location.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.17,0:11:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha, roger. All squads, complete closure by 0230 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delta, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Echo, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Let's hurry to the designated point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Major, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Delta. We found unusual\Nobjects right in front of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the unusual objects? Describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Poles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many cylindrical poles, about thirty\Ninches long, are mounted on our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Charlie, Echo, anything unusual\Nin the area? About thirty inches—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Echo. We see a few dozen of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple cylindrical objects with nothing attached, about three feet apart from one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not see any explosives or wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are poles by this entrance of the village as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those? It's as if they form a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those poles for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they be religious objects for the Shan or the Va?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. She is already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Echo to Alpha. Major, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached the surveillance point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no signs of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So the place is deserted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alpha to Charlie. How does it look from the east side?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Charlie. No movement in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.93,0:13:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a plant in view, but no one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo to Alpha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also see the corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are multiple corpses near the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's light to the south end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, we're the farthest from there. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Package Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We confirm Package Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen. The illegal drug plant has already been neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only us and Package Romeo here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Package Romeo running at 10 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target is going to the jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta to Alpha. She's approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's stopped right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target seems to be holding a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now she's disappeared into the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Deckard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Target is holding a hostage, and she sliced off his ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hostage screamed, so he must be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shue Yan. She's using him to lure us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Delta the closest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right. Pursue the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But do {\i0}not{\i1} approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only capture the location of the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delta, roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All other squads, provide backup for Delta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delta to Alpha. We can't locate the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alpha to Echo. Do you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:15:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Echo. Hold for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have her in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you copy, Delta? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the name of Santa Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to counter every injustice with an iron hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost Murdoch and Garraty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper team, report!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost target, but one shot hit her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's aiming for our heads instead of our armored body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All squads, do you copy? Everyone except\Nsquad captains, take off your night vision device.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on a face mask and prepare for close-range combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly equip your face masks!\NWe need to go back up Delta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Echo to Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo, report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've located Package Drug Vault inside the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful. She most likely set a booby trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have fought on filthy Vietnamese\Nbattlefields many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have quite a bit of experience fighting in the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were in Guadalcanal, I'd use a mortar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or, if we were in Vietnam, napalm bombs, to burn down the whole forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with your dearest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Echo to Alpha. We've located a detonator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems we need to input a numeral code.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Package Romeo telling us we need to capture her for the unlock code?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Wait, Gardner. That is a trap itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Evacuate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. All Squad Echo members, immediately—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Gardner, there's something over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Squad E Captain. Wright is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy bullet pierced the bulletproof vest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Package Romeo's weapon is flechettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's using a musket to fire those poles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She came with an antique weapon to hunt us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw the muzzle blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We've got her! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She mounted the numerous poles as a silent declaration that she won't let any of us return alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All squads, retreat slowly and exit the forest.\NDo not let your guards down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanchez, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sniper team. We're\Nnow in retreat support position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move because of all these traps in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Stay and prepare for enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The squad immobilized in the forest is like a trapped rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can attack them from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sniper team, watch out! You'll get assaulted first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a shot in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went for her leg to avoid giving her a fatal injury, but she ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only make her fiercer, like a wounded tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right? We will evacuate as soon as Squad Alpha takes support position!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless! Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanchez, where are you? Respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Join up with the main unit immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're going to keep dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your little foxes, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I skin all the foxes in the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my hunt won't end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally caught up, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.92,0:21:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you where to come, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what kind of person I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer and everything will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, I keep remembering things\NI don't need to. I can't stand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Everything is playing into my hands, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the fate of everyone living in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.62,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ. It's just like what that fucking midget said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, you've been living in that town for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've immersed yourself in Roanapur too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as this case is over, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Revy? The conclusion is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Fabiola. To be honest,\NI'm scared of what's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what that Japanese man told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I {\i1}do{\i0} know you can do it, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lord does not save anyone. People like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.87,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is about to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.56,0:23:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The matter will come to light when the\NOpium Army soldiers start their morning patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, things will be settled before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What settlement, Rock? Do you have a real sense of what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm betting on that split second\Nthat will decide everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, do you realize you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I can see what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, at this point, I can't even tell whether you are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make out what time it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a dead man keeps talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even be sure whether I'm alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I finish the revenge, I can return\Nto that mansion where the orchids bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge never mattered to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I kept defying his orders,\NChang let me leave the town with the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.48,0:24:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.10,0:24:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Balalaika, upon understanding Chang's intentions,\Ndidn't finish off Roberta and instead let her escape very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.16,0:24:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, Chang's goal is not only to keep Roanapur hidden from the public eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also to use Roberta to ruin the U.S. Army's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.22,0:24:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a major site of drug production, and Roanapur is its export port.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:25:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By having Roberta attack the U.S. Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.08,0:25:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chang intended to keep the U.S. judicial\Nauthority away from the Golden Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.79,0:25:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that cannot be allowed to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.58,0:25:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, so tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.04,0:25:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is {\i1}your{\i0} goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.53,0:25:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.58,0:25:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They killed your dad and caused you grief, trying to take away everything from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.42,0:25:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I cannot forgive that—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.04,0:25:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta, you got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who you judge and punish, you won't be redeemed of your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.21,0:25:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.41,0:25:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you aren't going to end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.31,0:25:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.31,0:25:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this ends everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.55,0:25:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Young Master would never say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.13,0:25:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't end this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.75,0:25:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be rewarded this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.01,0:25:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.32,0:26:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your revenge to Roanapur?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.14,0:26:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That town led many people to ruin, yet I never saved any.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.58,0:26:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still feeling sorry about that Tokyo girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.87,0:26:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.93,0:26:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this time I {\i1}will{\i0} put an end to the\Nmisfortune that befalls the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.22,0:26:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking for a long time, Roberta, about what I should say when I find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.48,0:26:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But words can't convey anything. That was my conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.41,0:26:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.87,0:26:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet everything on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Roberta?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.75,0:26:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe, my bullet will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.93,0:26:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not die,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.41,0:26:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gamble will bring
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this long dance of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.94,0:26:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this chain of miserable revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.75,0:26:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to an end, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.96,0:26:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes, Roberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.56,0:27:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about us? What about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.31,0:27:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't return to your peaceful homeland anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.23,0:27:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave the twilight to join us in the dark night?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.11,0:27:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only way to settle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.09,0:27:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm glad I did. I learned one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.82,0:27:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, I now understand how you guys feel every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.10,0:27:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.81,0:27:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.77,0:27:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control my hands anymore!\NI didn't mean to fire back! Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.63,0:28:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.16,0:28:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.17,0:28:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though my bullet should have pierced through.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.21,0:28:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberta,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.66,0:28:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.17,0:28:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, you're bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.39,0:28:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.60,0:28:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.85,0:28:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master, you were hit by my bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.79,0:28:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let your gun down, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.77,0:28:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so realistic I almost fired a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.98,0:28:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The impact was far greater than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.75,0:28:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Snap out of it and give first aid to Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.68,0:28:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.99,0:28:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he alive? Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.16,0:28:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.51,0:28:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died once at my bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.33,0:28:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you, and so did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.81,0:28:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here is a winner. Only the sinners remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.33,0:29:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will share your burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.25,0:29:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will support you, and we'll live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.82,0:29:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.13,0:29:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.79,0:29:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rock, they're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.02,0:29:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the Americans capture their target?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.58,0:29:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems so. I see three stretchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.34,0:29:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.54,0:29:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is undoubtedly the optimal result.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.93,0:29:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Garcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I could save somebody at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.32,0:29:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.31,0:29:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.95,0:29:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we just got really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.06,0:29:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.07,0:29:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.11,0:30:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a fucker who manipulated Young Master to play "Cambodian roulette," all under the pretense of kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.55,0:30:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. I fired a blank,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.48,0:30:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a hollow brass counterfeit just like your specious magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.74,0:30:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never see someone like you or that town again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.80,0:30:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your waltz with the dead until the Lord gets tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.74,0:30:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have definitely attained something unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.64,0:30:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Cathy, put a lot of sugar and milk in my coffee, enough for a pancake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.27,0:30:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, how's your blood sugar level been recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.87,0:30:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring it. We only live once, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.80,0:30:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the secretary had a private lunch meeting with the National Security Advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.34,0:30:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll draw a clear line in the next Security Council meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.32,0:30:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shue Yan's custody and rights will be transferred to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.50,0:30:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yes, in front of the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.69,0:31:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would have surely infuriated the other party.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.63,0:31:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a cavalcade of four-letter words in a voice you'd hear ringing out in a French restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.89,0:31:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.21,0:31:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.48,0:31:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder who they thought they were up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.22,0:31:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.43,0:31:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.58,0:31:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Chang.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.42,0:31:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a belated bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.10,0:31:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many months have passed since then,\Nbut Roanapur hasn't changed in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.67,0:31:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money and guns decide the worth of everything. That's one fact that won't easily change.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.05,0:31:42.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,800)\be1}Though my body is worn out and weak
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.64,0:31:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere on this planet, someone outdid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.94,0:31:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.42,0:31:50.58,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Though the strength that I once had is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:59.29,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Now my eyes have learned to cry heavy tears
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.29,0:32:07.75,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Now my heart is beating with yours
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.75,0:32:15.77,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}In the midst of the night I survived
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.77,0:32:24.42,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Where the moon and stars could not be found
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.42,0:32:32.69,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}Now I see the brightest light on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.69,0:32:37.27,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}In this moment I exist
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.27,0:32:41.15,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}In this moment I live
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.15,0:32:56.69,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3500)\be1}All because of the grace you bestowed on me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.62,0:33:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it painful to keep looking at that town through the eyes of a living man?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.86,0:33:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, that's the path you chose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.38,0:33:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only other option is to die for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.45,0:33:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.77,0:33:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you could reach that point once.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.39,0:33:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.13,0:33:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not now, Revy. Sometime, eventually.
